            "parent_id": null,
            "unique_id": 27862,
            "directions": "You can start from either end, that is, from Saint Arnaud or from Hanmer Springs.  It's more usually started from Saint Arnaud to take advantage of a slight altitude difference and the prevailing winds.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Saint Arnaud is in the Upper Wairau Valley, 85 km from Nelson or 131 km from Picton via Blenheim.   Hanmer Springs is located 134 km north of Christchurch. Both ends are reachable by bus.",
