            "parent_id": null,
            "unique_id": 1107,
            "directions": "From the main Kokopelli Trails parking lot, turn left and ride over the hill.  Turn right onto Mary's loop and ride Mary's past the Horsethief Bench cut-off.  You'll see a signed turn for &quot;Wrangler,&quot; but keep going.  About a mile further down there will be another signed single track turn off on the right for Wrangler.  Turn here, following the signs.  Stay on Wrangler all the way down a bomber downhill, bearing left at the final sign to head back to the gravel road.",
