            "directions": "Take US 287 north from Ft. Collins or south from Laramie, WY to Red Feather Lakes Road (CR 74E).  Go west 24-25 miles on Red Feather Lakes Rd., which will then turn into CR 73C.  Continue another 4-5 miles to Beaver Meadows Resort Ranch entry.  Go to gift shop underneath the restaurant, check in, and get a map. ",
